            <h3>
              For investors who would like to build and preserve their savings and wants positive social impact
            </h3>
            <p><strong>Higher Returns</strong><br />- compared to time deposit of commercial banks and government treasury bills</p>
            <p><strong>Invested in Strong Institutions in the Philippines</strong><br />- mainly in microfinance institutions and social enterprises</p>
            <p><strong>Professionally Managed</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
